{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": true, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248385, "create_time": 1655973161, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "““””", "timestamp": 1655973161}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248423, "create_time": 1655973713, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "（前）现代，，，", "timestamp": 1655973713}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248425, "create_time": 1655973730, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "党要管党，全面从严治党\n他们是这么说的", "timestamp": 1655973730}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248431, "create_time": 1655973781, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Carol: 抓着自己的头发飞起来，，，", "timestamp": 1655973781}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248486, "create_time": 1655974650, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "马克思的语境下国家本来就是阶级统治的工具，指望被统治阶级监督统治阶级，是唯心的想法。", "timestamp": 1655974650}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248496, "create_time": 1655974878, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "“似乎并没有监督和限制公权力的机制” 在历史唯物主义的视角里这根本不成为问题，因为既然国家都是阶级统治的工具，所以直接丢掉了被统治阶级监督统治阶级的幻想。", "timestamp": 1655974878}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248505, "create_time": 1655975187, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "“公权力”和“公民”二元对立，这是西方模糊了“阶级”后创造的政治话语体系，于是才能延伸出“监督和限制公权力”的话题。", "timestamp": 1655975187}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 248531, "create_time": 1655975756, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "列宁主义政党统治的国家是这样的", "timestamp": 1655975756}], "create_time": 1655973111, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": true, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1655975756, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 8, "pid": 71219, "poll": null, "reply": 8, "text": "", "timestamp": 1655973111}}